BX.GRT.EXTA.CD.WD-reservesOtherItems.def: Grants are defined as legally binding commitments that obligate a specific value of funds available for disbursement for which there is no repayment requirement. Data are in current U.S. dollars.
BX.GRT.EXTA.CD.WD-reservesOtherItems.name: Grants, excluding technical cooperation
BX.GRT.EXTA.CD.WD-reservesOtherItems.source: World Bank, International Debt Statistics, and OECD.
BX.GRT.EXTA.CD.WD-reservesOtherItems.dataset: World Bank, International Debt Statistics, and OECD.

BX.GRT.TECH.CD.WD-reservesOtherItems.def: Technical cooperation grants include free-standing technical cooperation grants, which are intended to finance the transfer of technical and managerial skills or of technology for the purpose of building up general national capacity without reference to any specific investment projects; and investment-related technical cooperation grants, which are provided to strengthen the capacity to execute specific investment projects. Data are in current U.S. dollars.
BX.GRT.TECH.CD.WD-reservesOtherItems.name: Technical cooperation grants
BX.GRT.TECH.CD.WD-reservesOtherItems.source: World Bank, International Debt Statistics, and OECD.
BX.GRT.TECH.CD.WD-reservesOtherItems.dataset: World Bank, International Debt Statistics, and OECD.

FI.RES.TOTL.CD-reservesOtherItems.def: Total reserves comprise holdings of monetary gold, special drawing rights, reserves of IMF members held by the IMF, and holdings of foreign exchange under the control of monetary authorities. The gold component of these reserves is valued at year-end (December 31) London prices. Data are in current U.S. dollars.
FI.RES.TOTL.CD-reservesOtherItems.name: Total reserves
FI.RES.TOTL.CD-reservesOtherItems.source: International Monetary Fund, International Financial Statistics and data files.
FI.RES.TOTL.CD-reservesOtherItems.dataset: International Monetary Fund, International Financial Statistics and data files.

FI.RES.TOTL.DT.ZS-reservesOtherItems.def: International reserves to total external debt stocks.
FI.RES.TOTL.DT.ZS-reservesOtherItems.name: Total reserves

FI.RES.TOTL.MO-reservesOtherItems.def: Total reserves comprise holdings of monetary gold, special drawing rights, reserves of IMF members held by the IMF, and holdings of foreign exchange under the control of monetary authorities. The gold component of these reserves is valued at year-end (December 31) London prices. This item shows reserves expressed in terms of the number of months of imports of goods and services they could pay for [Reserves/(Imports/12)].
FI.RES.TOTL.MO-reservesOtherItems.name: Total reserves in months of imports
FI.RES.TOTL.MO-reservesOtherItems.source: International Monetary Fund, International Financial Statistics and data files.
FI.RES.TOTL.MO-reservesOtherItems.dataset: International Monetary Fund, International Financial Statistics and data files.

FI.RES.XGLD.CD-reservesOtherItems.def: Total reserves minus gold comprise special drawing rights, reserves of IMF members held by the IMF, and holdings of foreign exchange under the control of monetary authorities. Gold holdings are excluded. Data are in current U.S. dollars.
FI.RES.XGLD.CD-reservesOtherItems.name: Total reserves minus gold
FI.RES.XGLD.CD-reservesOtherItems.source: International Monetary Fund, International Financial Statistics and data files.
FI.RES.XGLD.CD-reservesOtherItems.dataset: International Monetary Fund, International Financial Statistics and data files.
